    <item>
      <title>Instagram 热门账号浏览量因元信息回避政治而下降</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/instagram-shunning-politics-reduced-views-for-major-accounts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一项新研究发现，在 Meta Platforms Inc. 采取措施控制应用程序上的政治内容后的几个月内，几个著名的进步 Instagram 账户的覆盖率平均下降了 65%。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-12/instagram-shunning-politics-reduced-views-for-major-accounts</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 12 Aug 2024 13:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
